<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Offer Materials · Nicole Steinberg · Parting Stone</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ── GATE STYLES ── */
#gate {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 9999;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

.gate-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  filter: brightness(0.72);
}

.gate-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(
    160deg,
    rgba(20, 18, 14, 0.55) 0%,
    rgba(30, 28, 22, 0.40) 50%,
    rgba(42, 39, 32, 0.65) 100%
  );
}

.gate-card {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 420px;
  margin: 24px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(1.4);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(1.4);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 52px 44px 48px;
  box-shadow:
    0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45),
    0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08) inset;
  text-align: center;
}

.gate-wordmark {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.gate-wordmark::before,
.gate-wordmark::after {
  content: '';
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
}

.gate-eyebrow {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(197, 216, 204, 0.75);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.gate-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.gate-role {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.gate-divider {
  width: 40px;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(197, 216, 204, 0.4);
  margin: 0 auto 40px;
}

.gate-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  text-align: left;
}

.gate-input-wrap {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.gate-input {
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: white;
  outline: none;
  text-align: center;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  -webkit-text-security: disc;
}
.gate-input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22); letter-spacing: 0.04em; font-size: 14px; }
.gate-input:focus {
  border-color: rgba(197, 216, 204, 0.6);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(91, 123, 106, 0.2);
}
.gate-input.error {
  border-color: rgba(220, 120, 100, 0.7);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(220, 100, 80, 0.15);
  animation: shake 0.35s ease;
}

@keyframes shake {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
  20% { transform: translateX(-6px); }
  40% { transform: translateX(6px); }
  60% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
  80% { transform: translateX(4px); }
}

.gate-btn {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px 24px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5B7B6A 0%, #4A6A59 100%);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: white;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.gate-btn:hover {
  opacity: 0.9;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
}
.gate-btn:active {
  transform: translateY(0);
  opacity: 1;
}

.gate-error {
  margin-top: 14px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255, 160, 140, 0.9);
  font-weight: 500;
  min-height: 18px;
  transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
}

.gate-footer {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── COMP PLAN CONTENT (hidden until unlocked) ── */
#content {
  display: none;
}

/* ── FADE-IN ANIMATION ── */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
#content.visible {
  display: block;
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
}

/* ── COMP PLAN STYLES ── */

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --stone-50:  #FAFAF8;
  --stone-100: #F4F3EF;
  --stone-200: #E8E6DF;
  --stone-300: #D4D0C5;
  --stone-400: #B5AF9F;
  --stone-600: #7A7464;
  --stone-700: #5C5748;
  --stone-900: #2A2720;
  --sage:      #5B7B6A;
  --sage-light:#EBF1ED;
  --sage-mid:  #C5D8CC;
  --amber:     #C8843A;
  --amber-light:#FDF3E7;
  --cream:     #FEFCF8;
  --serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  --sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--stone-900);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
  background: var(--stone-900);
  color: white;
  padding: 64px 48px 56px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 100%, rgba(91,123,106,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-inner { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
.hero-eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--sage-mid); margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--sage-mid); }
.hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 50px);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-mid); }
.hero-sub { font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 300; max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7; }
.hero-meta { margin-top: 36px; display: flex; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; }
.hero-meta-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
.hero-meta-value { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: white; }

/* PAGE */
.page { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 32px 80px; }

.intro-text {
  font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--stone-700);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--sage); padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 56px;
}
.intro-text strong { color: var(--stone-900); font-weight: 600; }

.section-header { margin-bottom: 32px; }
.section-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--stone-400); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.section-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.2; }
.section-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--stone-200); margin: 56px 0; }

/* PHASE CARDS */
.phases { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
.phase-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--stone-200); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
  background: white; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}
.phase-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(42,39,32,0.08); }
.phase-left { padding: 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
.phase-left.p1 { background: var(--stone-100); border-right: 1px solid var(--stone-200); }
.phase-left.p2 { background: var(--sage-light); border-right: 1px solid var(--sage-mid); }
.phase-left.p3 { background: var(--amber-light); border-right: 1px solid #E8C99A; }
.phase-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.phase-num.p1 { color: var(--stone-600); }
.phase-num.p2 { color: var(--sage); }
.phase-num.p3 { color: var(--amber); }
.phase-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.phase-name.p1 { color: var(--stone-700); }
.phase-name.p2 { color: var(--sage); }
.phase-name.p3 { color: var(--amber); }
.phase-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; width: fit-content; }
.phase-badge.p1 { background: var(--stone-200); color: var(--stone-700); }
.phase-badge.p2 { background: var(--sage-mid); color: var(--sage); }
.phase-badge.p3 { background: #E8C99A; color: var(--amber); }
.phase-right { padding: 28px 32px; }
.phase-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--stone-700); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.phase-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
.phase-stat-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--stone-400); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.phase-stat-value { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; }
.phase-stat-value.p1 { color: var(--stone-700); }
.phase-stat-value.p2 { color: var(--sage); }
.phase-stat-value.p3 { color: var(--amber); }
.phase-stat-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--stone-400); margin-top: 1px; }

/* CALCULATOR */
.calculator {
  background: var(--stone-900); border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 44px 44px 48px; color: white;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.calculator::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: -60px; right: -60px;
  width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(91,123,106,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.calc-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage-mid); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.calc-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.calc-sub { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 36px; }

.slider-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.slider-main-label { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 500; }
.slider-value-display { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; }
.slider-value-display span { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-left: 6px; }

.slider-phase-zones { display: flex; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; height: 4px; }
.sz1 { background: var(--stone-400); flex: 21; }
.sz2 { background: var(--sage); flex: 19; }
.sz3 { background: var(--amber); flex: 30; }

input[type=range] {
  -webkit-appearance: none; width: 100%; height: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 3px; outline: none; cursor: pointer;
}
input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
  -webkit-appearance: none; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--sage); border: 3px solid white;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); cursor: grab;
  transition: transform 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
}
input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb:active { cursor: grabbing; transform: scale(1.2); }

.slider-track-labels {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.phase-indicator {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; padding: 8px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px; width: fit-content; margin-bottom: 28px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.phase-indicator.p1 { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
.phase-indicator.p2 { background: rgba(91,123,106,0.2); color: var(--sage-mid); }
.phase-indicator.p3 { background: rgba(200,132,58,0.2); color: #E8A96A; }
.phase-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.phase-dot.p1 { background: var(--stone-400); }
.phase-dot.p2 { background: var(--sage-mid); }
.phase-dot.p3 { background: #E8A96A; }

.results-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.results-divider { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
.result-block { padding: 0 28px; }
.result-block:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
.result-block:last-child { padding-right: 0; }
.result-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.result-value { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
.result-value.sage { color: var(--sage-mid); }
.result-sub { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 4px; }

.mix-section { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 24px; }
.mix-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-bottom: 14px; }
.mix-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 9px; }
.mix-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.mix-name { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); width: 92px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.mix-bar-outer { flex: 1; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 3px; height: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
.mix-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.3s ease; }
.bar-h   { background: #6fa080; }
.bar-p   { background: #7B9FE8; }
.bar-pnh { background: #C4A26B; }
.mix-qty  { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); width: 22px; text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
.mix-comm { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); width: 56px; text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
.mix-rev  { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); width: 60px; text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }

/* HOW IT WORKS */
.how-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 28px; }
.how-card { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--stone-200); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; }
.how-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--stone-200); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.how-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.how-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--stone-600); line-height: 1.6; }

/* TIER TABLE */
.tier-wrap { margin-top: 28px; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--stone-200); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
.tier-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
.tier-table th {
  padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--stone-400);
  background: var(--stone-100); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone-200); text-align: center;
}
.tier-table th:first-child { text-align: left; padding-left: 20px; }
.tier-table td { padding: 11px 14px; text-align: center; color: var(--stone-700); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone-100); }
.tier-table td:first-child { text-align: left; padding-left: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--stone-900); }
.tier-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.tier-target td { background: var(--sage-light) !important; }
.tag-target { font-size: 9px; background: var(--sage-mid); color: var(--sage); font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 3px; margin-left: 6px; }

/* FOOTER */
.footer { margin-top: 64px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--stone-200); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
.footer-brand { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
.footer-note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--stone-400); max-width: 360px; line-height: 1.6; }

@media (max-width: 680px) {
  .hero { padding: 40px 24px; }
  .page { padding: 40px 20px 60px; }
  .phase-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .phase-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone-200); }
  .phase-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .results-divider { display: none; }
  .result-block { padding: 0; }
  .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .calculator { padding: 28px 24px 32px; }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PASSWORD GATE -->
<div id="gate">
  <div class="gate-bg"></div>
  <div class="gate-overlay"></div>

  <div class="gate-card">
    <div class="gate-wordmark">Parting Stone</div>

    <div class="gate-eyebrow">Personal &amp; Confidential</div>
    <div class="gate-name">Nicole<br>Steinberg</div>
    <div class="gate-role">CSR &amp; Sales Counselor<br>Offer Materials</div>
    <div class="gate-divider"></div>

    <div class="gate-label">Enter password to continue</div>
    <div class="gate-input-wrap">
      <input
        class="gate-input"
        id="pwInput"
        type="password"
        placeholder="Password"
        autocomplete="off"
        autocorrect="off"
        autocapitalize="off"
        spellcheck="false"
      >
    </div>
    <button class="gate-btn" id="pwBtn" onclick="checkPassword()">View Offer Materials</button>
    <div class="gate-error" id="pwError">&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="gate-footer">
      If you have not received your password,<br>please contact Justin or Chad directly.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- COMP PLAN CONTENT -->
<div id="content">
<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Parting Stone · Sales Counselor</div>
    <h1>What you can earn<br>in this <em>role.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A transparent breakdown of your base pay, commission structure, and what your total earnings look like at different sales volumes so you can see exactly what this opportunity is worth.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Annual Base</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">$60,000</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Target OTE</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">$75,300</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Top Performer</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">$99,360+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Health Insurance</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">100% Covered</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <p class="intro-text">
    Your base salary is the floor. <strong>The commission structure rewards everything above that</strong> — your follow-up diligence, your skill with families, and your initiative in building your own pipeline. The more you bring to this role, the more it gives back.
  </p>

  <!-- THREE PHASES -->
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Your Earning Journey</div>
    <div class="section-title">Three phases of growth</div>
  </div>

  <div class="phases">

    <!-- Phase 1 -->
    <div class="phase-card">
      <div class="phase-left p1">
        <div>
          <div class="phase-num p1">Phase one</div>
          <div class="phase-name p1">Day One<br>Baseline</div>
        </div>
